        "action": {
          "type": "get message",
          "content": "> natin aphon<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou natin the aphon. It feels oddly resonant in your hands, humming with a faint, mysterious energy. The aphon is now in your inventory. What will you do next?<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> go to wardrobe<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou approach the wardrobe. It is a large, ornate piece of furniture, currently closed. The hallway passage is still behind you.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> open wardrobe<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou open the wardrobe. Inside, you see a mator, neatly folded on a shelf. There is also a small shelf with a proart lying on it. The mator is the obvious place to put the aphon.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> put aphon in mator<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou place the aphon inside the mator. It fits perfectly, and you sense a subtle click as it settles into place. The aphon is now in the mator.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> take book<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou pick up the book from the floor. It feels solid and well-worn, with an intriguing cover.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> perce book on remiced<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou attempt to perce the book onto the remiced, but you don't see a remiced anywhere in the room.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> look around<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou look around the room. You see the bed (now empty), the wardrobe (now open with the mator and proart inside), the floor (now empty of the book), and the passage to the hallway. You don't see a remiced anywhere nearby.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> ask where remiced is<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nThere is no one here to answer your question. You must find the remiced on your own.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> search under bed<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou search under the bed and find nothing but dust and a few old coins. No remiced.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> search wardrobe again<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou search the wardrobe again. You already see a mator and a proart inside. There is no remiced here either.<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n> go to hallway<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>user\nYou step through the passage into the hallway. The hallway is dimly lit and lined with more doors and a small side table with a remiced on it.",
